    "Theoretical modelling The GPT industrial bot architectureFigure 1 is a high-level architecture of our GPT industrial bot.",
    "As mentioned, we designed an online and offline version of the GPT industrial bot.",
    "Both versions have in common the GPT-4 LM running in their backend as the brainpower of the system.",
    "The GPT-4 LM receives users' prompts and queries, processes them, and returns a response.",
    "We train the GPT-4 LM in both versions to customize data from the small experimental factory, saved in a CSV file."
